1 packet Raspberry, Amaranth & Blackcurrant Granola
1 packet berry compote
2 packet flaked almonds
1 Oat Milk

Heat a medium frying pan over medium-high heat. Toast flaked almonds, tossing, until golden,
2-3 minutes.

In a serving bowl, add a layer of raspberry, amaranth & blackcurrant granola (store leftover granola in an airtight container).

Pour some oat milk over granola. Top with berry compote. Sprinkle with toasted almonds to serve.

FRESH TIP: Drizzle over your favourite nut butter!